name: Length, width and weight of Echinotrix diadema and E. Calamaris species sampled in Mombasa Marine National Park (Kenya) from December 1994 to March 1995
description: This dataset contains length, width and weight measurements of Echinotrix diadema and E. Calamaris sampled in Mombasa Marine National Park (Kenya) from December 1994 to March 1995. Animals were collected collected at low tidein the reef lagoonand in the channel on the Northern sideof Mombasa island, in front of theKenya Marine Fishery and Research Institute (K.M.F.R.I.). Collection was done while snorkeling, no SCUBAwas used. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Samyn, Y. (1995).Reproduction of two non-commercial sea urchins (Echinodermata: Echinoidea) in the MombasaMarine National Park, Kenya. MSc Thesis. Vrije Universiteit Brussel: Brussel. 134 pp.
